{"tid":1677394,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 即將有餐廳未能通過爆買壓力測試，賣到冇哂貨！","createTime":"2019-10-27T05:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T06:09:39.000Z","uid":19501,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d93e1c82f0c23fa465122365e0c88be5e45fd53f","tid":1677394,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:33:22.000Z","msg":"由於慈雲山嵐屋老闆缺乏理財哲學<br />\n公然將今日收入不扣除成本捐畀反華組織<br />\n<br />\n反對派認為已經令到做生意呢樣嘢變咗質<br />\n導致大量極端黃色消費份子流竄到店外排隊<br />\n以不文明手法表達對店主及一眾義工嘅不滿，現場群情洶湧<br />\n未到1點已經有超過十多名激進份子包圍餐廳<br />\n<br />\n樓主所見，大約12點已經損失1百碗牛丼，超過50碗豬丼<br />\n顯示舖頭極有可能未有足夠食材儲備，未來幾小時仲開唔開到舖展望負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pUvTdTL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpUvTdTL.png&h=5c796281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6js6yTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6js6yTR.jpg&h=93ec9f6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9916508a82b1d0c3c67a69ff82d39d6a609d25fd","tid":1677394,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d863946fbca0a8a2e532d2fdda29ee2c1f5c174f","tid":1677394,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf48bcf39d32920e5d585e355a91ed90ca434d59","tid":1677394,"uid":309121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8d659a86246ebb79b7de985b686522fa3f3a70","tid":1677394,"uid":304901,"like":